articles.

01:03:56.140 --> 01:03:59.760
Saying the board of,
you know, Jewish people

01:03:59.760 --> 01:04:01.120
in this town met,
and they had songs.

01:04:01.120 --> 01:04:03.510
And this person sang this song.

01:04:03.510 --> 01:04:06.690
Sometimes I'll actually find
a documented performance.

01:04:06.690 --> 01:04:11.650
But for this music
I'm not sure I would.

01:04:11.650 --> 01:04:13.410
&gt;&gt; I was thinking
more generally, not.

01:04:13.410 --> 01:04:14.710
&gt;&gt; Randall Goldberg: Yeah.

01:04:14.710 --> 01:04:16.010
&gt;&gt; Necessarily specifically.

01:04:16.010 --> 01:04:18.870
But was there, you know, was
there two-way communication?

01:04:18.870 --> 01:04:25.000
Was it mostly, you talked about
this network that existed.

01:04:25.000 --> 01:04:30.770
And how much support they felt
from what was happening here.

01:04:30.770 --> 01:04:33.490
&gt;&gt; Randall Goldberg: Oh, the
community back in Russia.

01:04:33.490 --> 01:04:34.790
&gt;&gt; Yes, yes.

01:04:34.790 --> 01:04:36.090
&gt;&gt; Randall Goldberg:
That's a good question.

01:04:36.090 --> 01:04:37.540
I know a lot of money
was raised.

01:04:37.540 --> 01:04:41.330
And there was a lot of money
and there was a lot of all kinds

01:04:41.330 --> 01:04:42.630
