01:04:42.630 --> 01:04:45.230
There was a lot of activity
in Washington about it.

01:04:45.230 --> 01:04:46.750
They really wanted
the U.S. government,

01:04:46.750 --> 01:04:49.530
people really wanted the U.S.
government to get involved.

01:04:49.530 --> 01:04:55.580
I'm not sure what happened
